nodes.name: History Paper Assignment
nodes.description:
Your mission students, should you choose to accept it, is to submit this assignment according to the instructions given to you. In this case, there is no assignment due date.

As always, should you or any of your fellow students be caught cheating or plagiarizing, your fellow classmates will disavow any knowledge of your actions, you will receive a 0 on this assignment, and additional disciplinary actions will ensue. This assignment will self-destruct in two weeks. Good luck, students.

- [Teacher Name]

 

Instructions for this assignment
Please choose any topic from U.S. History to write your research paper on and submit that research paper assignment here in Canvas.
